articles.author: Alana Wise
articles.title: 'No Kings' organizers project a massive turnout for this weekend's protests - NPR
articles.description: Organizers say they expect millions of Americans will march this weekend against the policies of the Trump administration. The protests come amid National Guard deployments in several cities.
articles.content: Organizers of the "No Kings" protests are projecting that millions of Americans will demonstrate against the policies of the Trump administration on Saturday, amid ongoing ICE arrests and the deploym… [+2532 chars]
